{"article_id":"wU9YcVkGIe2HUKCZ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"OTTAWA -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau will remain in power","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"but voters reduced his Liberal Party to a minority government Monday night .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"The Liberals took 156 seats of the 338 in the Canadian House of Commons .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"With less than 50 % of the seats in the House , Trudeau must reach out to the socialist New Democratic Party or the Quebec separatist Bloc Québécois","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to govern .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"In terms of the popular vote , the Conservatives outpolled the Liberals 34 % to 33 % .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"The result is a something of a surprise","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"given that the Conservatives were in the lead throughout most of the election","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that was called on Sept. 11 .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"( RELATED :","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Trudeau Calls Election","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"As Police Say","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"His Government Is Blocking Their Investigation Into SNC-Lavalin Scandal )","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"\" To my fellow Canadians it has been the greatest honour of my life to serve you for these past four years","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"and tonight you are sending us back to work for you , \"","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Trudeau told supporters in Montreal .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"\" We take this responsibility seriously","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"and we will work hard for you and your families ...","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"to those","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"who did not vote for us know","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that we will work every single day for you ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"we will govern for everyone .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Regardless of how you cast your ballot","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"ours is a team","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that will fight for all Canadians . \"","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Trudeau was hit by a blackface scandal early in the election campaign","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"that many thought","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"would end his political career .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Although he quickly apologized for the first picture , more pictures and videos soon emerged","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"and Trudeau told reporters","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that he couldn ' t remember","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"if there were other images still unaccounted for .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"For the remainder of the campaign Trudeau focused on issues like gun control and climate change .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Late in the campaign , former President Barack Obama endorsed Trudeau","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"- an unprecedented move by a former president .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Trudeau would not say","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"whether he or his campaign had solicited the endorsement from Obama .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"( RELATED :","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Trudeau Plans ' To Ban Military-Style Assault Rifles '","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Critics Ask ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Meaning What ? )","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"The Conservative Party remains the Official Opposition","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"and gained over 20 more seats in the House of Commons .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"Conservative Leader Andrew Scheer said","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"he is ready for a rematch :","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"\" Mr . Trudeau ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"when your government falls ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Conservatives will be ready","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"and we will win , \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"At the October 7 leader ' s debate , Scheer focused on Trudeau ' s apparent disconnect between his persona life and pubic persona .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"\" He ' s very good at pretending things .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"He can ' t even remember","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"how many times he put blackface on","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"because the fact of the matter is he ' s always wearing a mask .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"He puts on a reconciliation mask","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"and then fires the attorney general , the first one of Indigenous background .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"He puts on a feminist mask","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"and then fires two strong female employees","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"for not going along with his corruption , \"","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Scheer said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":127,"left":0,"right":126,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":106,"right":125,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":77,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":68,"right":76,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":65,"right":67,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":3,"right":66,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":66,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":71,"right":75,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":6,"right":70,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":7,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":10,"right":74,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":11,"right":73,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":12,"right":72,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":105,"left":88,"right":104,"relation":"joint","nuclearity"